            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "uncommon",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Ingested:} A creature subjected to this poison must succeed on a Intelligence saving throw (DC 14) or become {@condition poisoned} for {@dice 2d4} hours. While {@condition poisoned}, the creature has disadvantage on attack rolls and ability checks."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Hallucinating Spore (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Inhaled:} A creature hit by this poison and each creature within 5 feet of it must make a Wisdom save (DC 16). On a failed save it takes {@damage 3d10} psychic damage and becomes {@condition poisoned} for 1 minute."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Midnight Tears (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Ingested:} A creature that ingests this poison suffers no effect until the stroke of midnight. If the poison has not been neutralized before then, the creature must succeed on a Constitution save (DC 17) or take {@damage 10d10} poison damage."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Wild Magic Poison (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Injure:} A creature subjected to this poison suffers one of the effects described in the following table (roll {@dice 1d4} to determine the effect).",
                {
                    "type": "table",
                    "colLabels": [
                        "Dice Result",
                        "Poison Effect"
                    ],
                    "colStyles": [
                        "col-2 text-center",
                        "col-10"
                    ],
                    "rows": [
                        [
                            "1",
                            "It must succeed on a Constitution save (DC 16). It takes {@damage 5d10} lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much on a successful save."
                        ],
                        [
                            "2",
                            "It must succeed on a Wisdom save (DC 16) or use its turn to move within 5 feet of its nearest ally and make an attack against it."
                        ],
                        [
                            "3",
                            "It must succeed on a Constitution save (DC 16). On a failed save it is {@condition stunned} until the end of its next turn. On a successful save it is {@condition incapacitated} for 1 minute."
                        ],
                        [
                            "4",
                            "The target takes {@damage 3d10} lightning damage and must succeed on a Constitution save (DC 16) or become {@condition restrained} until the end of its next turn."
                        ]
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Yugoloth Blood (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Injure:} A creature hit by this poison must succeed on a Constitution save (DC 16). On a failed save, it takes {@damage 5d8} necrotic damage and is {@condition poisoned} for 1 minute."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Avernus' Kiss (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "very rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Injure:} A creature subjected to this poison takes {@damage 6d6} fire damage. For 1 minute, at the start of its turn, the creature takes {@damage 6d6} fire damage and must make a Dexterity save (DC 18) or be {@condition restrained}."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Black Dragon Breath (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "very rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Inhaled:} A creature hit by this poison and each creature within 10 feet of it, must succeed on a Constitution save DC 18 taking {@damage 10d8} acid damage on a failed save, or half as much on a successful one."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Lolth Bite (TAF)",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "G",
            "rarity": "very rare",
            "entries": [
                "{@i Injure:} A creature subjected to this poison takes {@damage 8d8} necrotic damage and must make Wisdom save (DC 18), or become {@condition incapacitated} and have its speed reduced to 0."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Blade of Immolation",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "M",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "bonusWeapon": true,
            "entries": [
                "You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this weapon, and on a hit, it deals an extra {@damage 1d6} fire damage. When you score a critical hit using this weapon, the target catches fire.",
                "{@b Invoking the Rune.} When you hit with this weapon, you can use your reaction to invoke its rune. Doing so increases the extra fire damage dealt to {@damage 2d6}. Once the rune has been invoked, it can't be invoked again until the next dawn."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Bow of Conflagration",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "R",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "bonusWeapon": true,
            "entries": [
                "Ammunition fired from this bow blazes brightly. You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made using the weapon. When you hit using this weapon, the target and each creature of your choice that you can see within 5 feet of the target must succeed on a DC 13 Dexterity save or catch fire, taking {@damage 1d6} fire damage."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Bow of Melodies",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "R",
            "rarity": "very rare",
            "entries": [
                "This bow has multiple strings and resembles a lyre or small harp. If you're proficient in Performance, you gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made using the weapon. This bonus increases to +2 if you're also proficient in Insight."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Divine Touched Weapon",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "rarity": "varies",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "entries": [
                "This weapon has been touched by divine power, blessed by a saint or wielded by a holy hero.",
                "{@b Slumbering (Uncommon).} Once every turn, when you hit with this weapon, you can choose a creature other than you within 30 feet of you and grant it temporary hit points equal to your proficiency bonus.",
                "{@b Stirring (Rare).} You gain a +1 on attack and damage rolls made with this weapon. Once every turn, when you hit with this weapon, you can cause one of the following effects.",
                {
                    "type": "list",
                    "items": [
                        "{@b Holy Strike.} The target of the attack takes {@damage 1d12} extra radiant damage.",
                        "{@b Holy Heal.} You can choose a creature other than you within 30 feet of you and grant it temporary hit points equal to {@dice 1d12} + your proficiency bonus."
                    ]
                },
                "{@b Wakened (Very Rare).} It has and improves the Stirring property. The bonus to attack and damage rolls increases to +2. In addition, when you use either of the effects granted by the Stirring property, you can use it twice per turn instead of once."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Dragon Wrath Weapon",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "rarity": "varies",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "entries": [
                "This weapon can absorb the energy of a chromatic or metallic dragon's breath weapon.",
                "{@b Slumbering (Uncommon).} When you score a critical hit with this weapon, each creature of your choice within 5 feet of you takes 5 points of acid, cold, fire, lightning, or poison damage (your choice).",
                "{@b Stirring (Rare).} It has the Slumbering property. In addition, you gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made using the weapon. On a hit, the weapon deals an extra {@damage 1d6} damage of the type chosen for the Slumbering property.",
                "{@b Wakened (Very Rare).} It has the Slumbering property, and it improves on the Stirring property. The bonus to attack and damage rolls increases to +2, and the extra damage dealt by the Stirring property increases to {@damage 2d6}."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Fool's Blade",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "M",
            "rarity": "very rare",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "bonusWeapon": true,
            "entries": [
                "You gain a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. The blade has 6 charges and regains {@dice 1d6} expended charges daily at dawn.",
                "{@b Fool's Feint.} You can feint to target your enemy's weak points. When you hit a creature with this weapon, you can spend 1 charge to deal {@damage 2d12} extra psychic damage.",
                "{@b Misdirect.} When a creature within 60 feet of you targets you with an attack, you can use a reaction to spend 1 charge and force that creature to make a DC 17 Intelligence saving throw. On a failed save, the creature must target a different creature."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Gem Infused Weapon",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "rarity": "varies",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "entries": [
                "This weapon is fashioned from the horn or claw of a gem dragon and can channel its power.",
                "{@b Slumbering (Uncommon).} The weapon has 4 charges and regains {@dice 1d4} expended charges at dawn. When you hit a creature using this weapon, you can expend 1 charge to regain a number of hit points equal to {@dice 1d6}.",
                "{@b Stirring (Rare).} It has the Slumbering property and it makes you regain {@dice 1d10} extra hit points. In addition, when you hit with an attack roll using this sword, the target takes an extra {@damage 1d10} psychic damage.",
                "{@b Wakened (Very Rare).} It has and improves the Stirring property. Both the healing and extra damage of the Stirring property increase to {@dice 2d10}."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Nyx's Mirror Feather",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "M",
            "weaponCategory": "simple",
            "rarity": "common",
            "entries": [
                "This glowing plume can be wielded like a weapon. While holding a weapon in one hand and this item in the other, unless this weapon is the product of a spell, the feather becomes a perfect duplicate of that weapon."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Nyx's Sheath of Homecoming",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "M",
            "rarity": "common",
            "entries": [
                "Nyx used this sheath as a perch to take a little nap, when she left, it became so heartbroken that it has abandonment issues. You can sheath a weapon with the thrown property in it. If you throw the weapon, it returns to the sheath at the end of your turn."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Primal Force Weapon",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "rarity": "varies",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "entries": [
                "This weapon channels the power of nature, forged by an archfey or crafted from a divine tree.",
                "{@b Slumbering (Uncommon).} Once every turn, when you hit a creature with this weapon, you can push or pull it 5 feet from you horizontally.",
                "{@b Stirring (Rare).} It has the Slumbering property. In addition, you gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made using the weapon. When you hit with this weapon you can deal {@damage 1d8} extra damage of the weapon's type.",
                "{@b Wakened (Very Rare).} It has the Slumbering property and improves the Stirring property. In addition, the bonus to attack and damage rolls increases to +2, and the damage dealt by the Stirring property increases to {@damage 2d8}."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Starshot Bow",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "R",
            "rarity": "rare",
            "reqAttune": true,
            "entries": [
                "The weapon has 4 charges and regains {@dice 1d4} expended charges daily at dawn. When you hit using this weapon, you can spend 1 charge to activate one of the following features.",
                "{@b Balance.} A creature of your choice within 60 feet of you can regain hit points equal to {@dice 2d8} plus your proficiency bonus.",
                "{@b Flames.} Until the end of your next turn, when you hit using this weapon, the attack deals an additional {@damage 2d8} fire damage.",
                "{@b Rogue.} Until the end of your next turn, you have the {@condition invisible} condition, and anything you are wearing or carrying is also invisible."
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Wand of the War Mage",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "type": "WD",
            "rarity": "varies",
            "reqAttune": "by a spellcaster",
            "entries": [
                "While holding this wand, you gain a bonus to your spell attack rolls and spell save DC determined by the wand's rarity. In addition, your spell attacks ignore Half Cover.",
                "{@b Uncommon.} +1 bonus on your spell attack rolls and spell save DC.",
                "{@b Rare.} +2 bonus on your spell attack rolls and spell save DC.",
                "{@b Very Rare.} +3 bonus on your spell attack rolls and spell save DC."
            ]
        }
    ],
